name: Rick
line: Whoa whoa wh-what are you doing to me?

name: Rick
line: The United Nations, where every human is an animal. But I thought, you know, nobody wants to say "I'm an animal" when talking about politics.

name: Agent
line: Well, I don't think you do.

name: Agent
line: Yeah, you think I'm that way about animal rights, too?

name: Rick
line: I don't care about family or community. I just keep an eye on Morty.

name: Agent
line: All right, calm down, Morty. You're scaring the Vindicators.

name: Agent
line: You're scarily fast, Morty, they know I've been scaring 'em since I got them. You know, they're just babies. They know I mean it's scary.

name: Rick
line: Rick, I can't believe we're sitting around, standing around in Mr. Goldenfold's house. It's really weird.

name: Agent
line: Goldenfold's just like that movie that's scary stuff. It made me a little sad.
